{"tid":2231812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"智利抗暴｜警員扔年輕示威者落橋被捕 遭控企圖謀殺並涉作假證供","createTime":"2020-10-06T02:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T03:23:33.000Z","uid":44209,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"af41fdba944d4760fb5a0965b01f6c57f2dd7b7d","tid":2231812,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"智利即將舉行修憲公投，首都聖地牙哥上周爆發示威及警民衝突，一名16歲示威者被警員從橋上丟入河，惹起公憤。當局表示已拘捕一名涉事警員，他被控企圖謀殺。<br />\n<br />\n被扔入馬普丘河（Rio Mapocho）的16歲男青年目前情況穩定，有創傷性腦損傷及手腕骨折。當局已拘捕一名警員，檢方除指控他企圖謀殺，也涉作假證供。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201006/SXX24J4WJRG7JDWWP6SKW4HMLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201006%2FSXX24J4WJRG7JDWWP6SKW4HMLU%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=bbd25502\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201006%2FSXX24J4WJRG7JDWWP6SKW4HMLU%2F&h=eb6287b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201006/SXX24J4WJRG7JDWWP6SKW4HMLU/</a>"},{"pid":"50bed0f5eea8482a39bbd795e0e3a369a8c814e9","tid":2231812,"uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39JnVf3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39JnVf3.gif&h=23f00b28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c044012e5061e13ebccf379b623a540b70e05ea","tid":2231812,"uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exZZc3t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexZZc3t.gif&h=9dce90fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcc9096a950e70210fdb012d3d244fb11cf7e768","tid":2231812,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:02:15.000Z","msg":"做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"